title: Walter Desmaison
text: Walter Desmaison (born 18 October 1991 in <a href="Girac">Girac</a>, <a href="France">France</a>) is a <a href="French%20people">French</a> professional <a href="rugby%20union">rugby union</a> player. He plays at <a href="prop%20%28rugby%20union%29">prop</a> for <a href="Racing%20M%C3%A9tro%2092">Racing Métro</a> in the <a href="Top%2014">Top 14</a>.
